######################################################################


Attention: if running occured error, please reboot operating system.


#########################  Running All ###############################


## Runing all of adidemo.
    
    1.Upload driver.

    ==>init.sh --[sensor type]

    example:
        #init.sh --imx222

    2.Need input command.
    ==>adidemo -a


#######################  Option Running  #############################


## Use VLC to preview video.

    1.Upload driver.

    ==>init.sh --[sensor type]

    example:
        #init.sh --imx222

    2.Fristly, need running rtsp_server and start video.
    
    input command:

    ==>rtsp_server &
    ==>adidemo -m
    ==>video -IOS0
    
    3.Second, use VLC access. 

    In VLC, down CTL + N. Input "rtsp://<IP of board>/stream1" in URL.

    example: rtsp://192.168.10.162/stream1


## Run ISP
    
    1.Input command when video is start.

    ==>isp -IOS

## Run osd
    
    1.Input command when video is start.

    ==>osd -IO

    2.More operation, please input command.

    ==>osd -h

## Run PDA

    1.Need initalize OSD.

    ==>osd -IO

    2.Running PDA.

    ==>pda -I 0
    ==>pda -OS

    3.More operation, please input command.

    ==>pda -h

## Run IR

    1.Running IR.

    ==>ir open <node path>
    example:
        ir open /dev/input/event0

    2.More operation, please input command.

    ==>ir help

## Runing audio

    1. Initalize audio.

    ==>audio -I

    2. Running audio.

    ==>audio -L

    3.More operation, please input command.

    ==>audio -h

## Running PWM

    1. Initalize PWM

    ==>pwm -I -O 0 -m 0 -s 1000 -d 500

    2. Start PWM.

    ==>pwm -S
    
    3.More operation, please input command.

    ==>pwm -h

## Running PM

    1.More operation, please input command.

    ==>pm -h

